'''John Milne''' was an [[English people|English]] [[association football|footballer]] who played in [[the Football League]] for [[Manchester City F.C.|Ardwick]] and [[Bolton Wanderers F.C.|Bolton Wanderers]].<ref>{{cite book|last=Joyce|first=Michael|title=Football League Players' Records 1888 to 1939|year=2004|publisher=SoccerData|isbn=1-899468-67-6}}</ref>

